      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">25.504-1</ph> Buy American statute.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1635e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1657e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d1635e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1657e15" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Example
1</i>.</p>
                     <table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                        <tgroup cols="3"
                                colsep="1"
                                rowsep="1"
                                outputclass="Notitle_rule"
                                class="- topic/tgroup ">
                           <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="19*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="21*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colwidth="60*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                              <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer A</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry "> 
                                    $16,000
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">Domestic end product, small business</entry>
                              </row>
                              <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer B</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry "> 
                                    $15,700
                                 </entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">Domestic end product, small business</entry>
                              </row>
                              <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer C</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">$10,000</entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">U.S.-made end product (not domestic), small
business</entry>
                              </row>
                           </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                     </table>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1657e49" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Analysis:</i> This
acquisition is for end products for use in the United States and
is set aside for small business concerns. The Buy American statute
applies. Since the acquisition value is less than $25,000 and the
acquisition is set aside, none of the trade agreements apply. Perform
the steps in <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(a). Offer C is
evaluated as a foreign end product because it is the product of
a small business, but is not a domestic end product (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(c)(4)). Since Offer
B is a domestic offer, apply the 30 percent factor
to Offer C (see <xref href="25.105.dita#FAR_25_105"
                              base="i1093701"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.105</xref>(b)(2)). The resulting
evaluated price of $13,000 remains
lower than Offer B. The cost of Offer B is therefore unreasonable
(see <xref href="25.105.dita#FAR_25_105"
                              base="i1093701"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.105</xref>(c)). Award on Offer
C at $10,000 (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(c)(4)(i)).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1657e72" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d1635e126" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1657e77" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Example
2</i>.</p>
                     <table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                        <tgroup cols="3"
                                colsep="1"
                                rowsep="1"
                                outputclass="Notitle_rule"
                                class="- topic/tgroup ">
                           <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="18*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="19*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colwidth="63*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                           <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                              <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer A</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">$11,000</entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">Domestic end product, small business</entry>
                              </row>
                              <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer B</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">$10,700</entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">Domestic end product, small business</entry>
                              </row>
                              <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
                                 <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">Offer C</entry>
                                 <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">$10,200</entry>
                                 <entry colname="3" class="- topic/entry ">U.S.-made end product (not domestic), small
business</entry>
                              </row>
                           </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                     </table>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1657e111" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Analysis</i>:
This acquisition is for end products for use in the United States
and is set aside for small business concerns. The Buy American statute
applies. Perform the steps in <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(a).
Offer C is evaluated as a foreign end product because it is the
product of a small business but is not a domestic end product (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(c)(4)). After applying
the 30 percent  factor,
the evaluated price of Offer C is $13,260. Award on
Offer B at $10,700 (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">25.502</xref>(c)(4)(ii)).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
